唔會好像黑警集團 咁一面倒<br />\n<br />\n有3個主要原因<br />\n<br />\n1.  統戰力度<br />\n支那共產黨統戰重點唔係消防<br />\n果堆咩交流團，返支那上堂<br />\n消防唔係無  但少好多<br />\n<br />\n2.14年因素<br />\n叫有良心的黃警退出黑警集團<br />\n某程度快而加快左警察的敗壞<br />\n<br />\n但消防無呢個情況<br />\n反而好多黃警 14年後 轉投 消防等其他紀律部隊<br />\n<br />\n3. 對抗程緒<br />\n對抗程緒很多時只有一邊係搞唔起<br />\n因為消防普遍 無受到 市民敵意<br />\n所以內部種敵視市民反彈都比較輕"},{"pid":"e52efb5b8fa88f21de0e1e16a91186453d61a38f","tid":1399524,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d3b4881d77427c994fb2ac4e7a480c7adb6f5d9d","tid":1399524,"uid":91721,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:13:25.000Z","msg":"毅進畢業生<br />\n同毅進仔係兩樣野嚟"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:27:09.000Z","msg":"我覺得讀毅進就已經被人標籤咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a948a8ff7d8c520b3be2d5f796a4e859f0fbf58d","tid":1399524,"uid":21937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"好簡單 一個弱智仔 你比好大權佢 咪好撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都無足夠既分析力<br />\n消防又無咩權 又唔可以拉你番去坐"},{"pid":"142661d971f93ca7ec9e0f3e55863d86e355a21b","tid":1399524,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a948a8ff7d8c520b3be2d5f796a4e859f0fbf58d","tid":1399524,"uid":21937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:30:25.000Z","msg":"好簡單 一個弱智仔 你比好大權佢 咪好撚大鑊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢都無足夠既分析力<br />\n消防又無咩權 又唔可以拉你番去坐"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:33:56.000Z","msg":"咁林鄭夠高學歷過班警察啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec4d957d7be9fdd2d9b31b88d2702d2fe555dc59","tid":1399524,"uid":21937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"142661d971f93ca7ec9e0f3e55863d86e355a21b","tid":1399524,"uid":169676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a948a8ff7d8c520b3be2d5f796a4e859f0fbf58d","tid":1399524,"uid":21937,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T08:30:25.000Z",